# Synergetics.ai Marketplace Platform — Task Breakdown

## Phase 1: Monorepo & Foundation
- [ ] Initialize Turborepo monorepo structure with all apps and packages
- [ ] Configure shared TypeScript, ESLint, Prettier configs
- [ ] Set up `packages/types` — shared Zod schemas & TypeScript types
- [ ] Set up `packages/utils` — shared utility functions
- [ ] Set up `packages/ui` — shadcn/ui shared component library (dark theme)
- [ ] Set up `packages/db` — Drizzle ORM schema, migrations, seed data
- [ ] Set up `packages/wallet` — Web3 wallet utilities
- [ ] Set up `packages/x402` — x402 protocol SDK
- [ ] Set up `packages/api-client` — typed API client
- [ ] Create `.env.example` with all variables documented

## Phase 2: Database Schema & Migrations
- [ ] Create Drizzle schemas for all entities (users, sellers, wallets, listings, etc.)
- [ ] Add indexes, constraints, relations
- [ ] Create seed data script
- [ ] Create MongoDB schemas (audit_logs, listing_metadata, analytics_events)

## Phase 3: API Server (Fastify)
- [ ] Set up Fastify 5.x with TypeScript
- [ ] Auth middleware (Clerk + SIWE)
- [ ] All REST endpoints (/auth, /listings, /categories, /cart, /checkout, /me, /seller, /admin, /x402, /webhooks)
- [ ] OpenAPI 3.1 auto-generation via @fastify/swagger
- [ ] Background jobs (BullMQ)
- [ ] Event bus (NATS JetStream)
- [ ] Request logging (pino) with correlation IDs
- [ ] Error handling middleware
- [ ] Health check endpoints

